### Psychological Safety Scale (Edmondson, 1999)
### instrumentId: PSS-Edmondson | instrumentVersion: 1999
### level_of_analysis: team | scoring.method: normative | single_construct: true
### Changes from v1:
###   - single_construct moved to template level (now in model schema)
###   - scoring.reverse_scored_items now in IScoringConfig (added to model)
###   - scoring.benchmarks now in IScoringConfig as Record<string, IBenchmarkBand>
###   - benchmarks.range changed from { range: [1.0, 3.5] } to [number, number] tuple
###   - Dropped: scoring.unit (redundant with level_of_analysis: team)
###   - Dropped: scoring.team_score_calculation (implementation detail, not schema)
###   - scale_range.labels changed to keyed Record<string, string> format
###   - scoring.reverse_score_formula moved to item level only (not duplicated on scoring root)

